	dprr:hasNoteText "Monetalis. In MRR 2.437, and Index, 557, refer also to Crawford RRC 1.318-319, no. 310, 118-107 B.C. Crawford distinguishes between the monetalis and the praetor and proconsul of the same name in 119 and 118 (MRR 1.526, 528), who is also RE no. 373.\n" ;
